Role/Purpose of ContextLoaderListener in Spring?
https://stackoverflow.com/questions/11815339/role-purpose-of-contextloaderlistener-in-spring

ContextLoaderListener is optional. You have to use it when you want to put your Servlet file in your custom location or with custom name, rather than the default name "[servlet-name]-servlet.xml" and path under "Web-INF/"

